snippet.title: The Imaginary Circle | Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2100830/The_Imaginary_Circle/?beta=0
The Imaginary Circle is a narrative experience, lasting about an hour and a half, in which you must find your way around an abandoned prison. 
Rummage through the documents, force open doors, call former employees, craft tools, but overall ask yourself: Should I use my only bullet now?
